txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Pure black skin from beasts and cave-claws surrounding Aughaire. Deliver the items to Raith at Aughaire in the south-western reaches of Angmar.
'We will ensure that these are used well. Thank you.'
'We can use the skin from the beasts and cave-claws to fashion important items for our people.'
Council of the North Task: Pure Black Skin
The Hillmen at Aughaire have requested a collection of pure black skin to be delivered to Raith.
Deliver the pure black skin to Raith at Aughaire in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver pure black skin from beasts and cave-claws surrounding Aughaire to Raith, a Hillman within the settlement.
Wanted: Pure black skin from beasts and cave-claws surrounding Aughaire.
